[size=150][b]Features[/b][/size]
[list]
[*] Items inside the main menu can be added/edited/deleted very easily without the need to edit the button code itself. Just open the main menu context menu (Right click inside the menu).
[*] Items inside the main menu can be rearranged by dragging them while holding down the Shift key.
[*] Items inside the main menu can be moved inside other menus by dragging them while holding down the Shift + Control/Command keys.
[*] Hotkeys can be assigned to any item.
[*] Items can be created inside other menus inside the main menu. An [i]infinite[/i] amount of menus can be created/nested.
[*] The snippets of text can contain any type of character (HTML/BBCode/XML tags, tab characters, line breaks, ASCII characters, etc.). The text will be inserted exactly how its seen in the items creation window.
[*] Several copies of Multi Snippets Inserter can be installed at the same time. Each button will have its separated menus stored in separated files.[/list]

